  "body_html": "<p>Notes:</p>\n<p>Rich vanilla</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Citrus</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Honeyed sugar </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">amber </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p data-start=\"341\" data-end=\"669\">Pure gourmand heaven.<br data-start=\"374\" data-end=\"377\">This is the ultimate choice for <strong data-start=\"409\" data-end=\"428\">gourmand lovers</strong> — delicious, comforting, and irresistibly feminine. It smells like <strong data-start=\"496\" data-end=\"508\">basbousa</strong>, the Ramadan dessert we all love: warm, sweet, buttery, and soaked in syrup. Cozy, nostalgic, and luxurious at the same time, like dessert served on fine china.</p>\n<p data-start=\"671\" data-end=\"690\"><strong data-start=\"671\" data-end=\"688\">When to Wear:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"691\" data-end=\"909\">\n<li data-start=\"691\" data-end=\"732\">\n<p data-start=\"693\" data-end=\"732\">Ramadan evenings &amp; post-iftar moments</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"733\" data-end=\"778\">\n<p data-start=\"735\" data-end=\"778\">Cozy family gatherings and relaxed nights</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"779\" data-end=\"833\">\n<p data-start=\"781\" data-end=\"833\">When you want to feel sweet, comforting, and loved</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"834\" data-end=\"909\">\n<p data-start=\"836\" data-end=\"909\">Perfect for anyone who wants to smell <strong data-start=\"874\" data-end=\"909\">edible, soft, and unforgettable</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong data-start=\"874\" data-end=\"909\">30ml</strong></p>",
